trans-unit.source: Represents the Dispatcher when it is in a disable state and provides a means to re-enable dispatcher processing.
trans-unit.target: Representa o Dispatcher quando ele está em um estado desabilitado e fornece um meio para reabilitar o processamento do dispatcher.

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.Windows.Threading.Dispatcher.DisableProcessing%2A> returns a DispatcherProcessingDisabled object when it is called.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Windows.Threading.Dispatcher.DisableProcessing%2A>Retorna um objeto DispatcherProcessingDisabled quando ele é chamado.</xref:System.Windows.Threading.Dispatcher.DisableProcessing%2A>

trans-unit.source: Disabling dispatcher processing is an advanced method that is intended to eliminate the chance of unrelated reentrancy.
trans-unit.target: Desabilitar o processamento do dispatcher é um método avançado que é destinado para eliminar a chance de reentrância não relacionada.

trans-unit.source: The effects of disabling processing are as follows: - [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_clr#initcap](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-clrsharpinitcap-md.md)] locks will not pump messages internally.
trans-unit.target: Os efeitos de desabilitar o processamento são os seguintes:- [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_clr#initcap](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-clrsharpinitcap-md.md)] bloqueios não bomba mensagens internamente.

trans-unit.source: - <xref:System.Windows.Threading.DispatcherFrame> objects are not allowed to be pushed.
trans-unit.target: - <xref:System.Windows.Threading.DispatcherFrame>objetos não podem ser enviados por push.</xref:System.Windows.Threading.DispatcherFrame>

trans-unit.source: - Message processing is not permitted.
trans-unit.target: -Processamento de mensagens não é permitido.

trans-unit.source: Calling <xref:System.Windows.Threading.DispatcherProcessingDisabled.Dispose%2A> on the DispatcherProcessingDisabled object will re-enable dispatcher processing.
trans-unit.target: Chamando <xref:System.Windows.Threading.DispatcherProcessingDisabled.Dispose%2A>no DispatcherProcessingDisabled objeto novamente habilitar o processamento do dispatcher.</xref:System.Windows.Threading.DispatcherProcessingDisabled.Dispose%2A>

trans-unit.source: Re-enables dispatcher processing.
trans-unit.target: Habilita o processamento do dispatcher novamente.

trans-unit.source: Disabling dispatcher processing is an advanced method that is intended to eliminate the chance of unrelated reentrancy.
